  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/50px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/75px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/100px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Abelar Hightower</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/50px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/75px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/100px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Dragon_and_the_Tower_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"The Dragon and the Tower by Even Mehl Amundsen.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/70/The_Dragon_and_the_Tower_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg/350px-The_Dragon_and_the_Tower_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/70/The_Dragon_and_the_Tower_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg/525px-The_Dragon_and_the_Tower_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/70/The_Dragon_and_the_Tower_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg/700px-The_Dragon_and_the_Tower_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Abelar and <a href=\"/index.php/Valarr_Targaryen\" title=\"Valarr Targaryen\">Valarr Targaryen</a>, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.evenamundsen.com/\">Even Mehl Amundsen</a> ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nthe <a href=\"/index.php/Hightower\" title=\"Hightower\">Hightower</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafabelar_hightower.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafabelar_hightower.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i> (appears)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nUncredited</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_(TV_series)\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms (TV series)\">A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Abelar Hightower</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abelar_Hightower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In the lists, Abelar wore clothes of <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> and smoke colors, with the <a href=\"/index.php/Hightower\" title=\"Hightower\">stone watchtower</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a> depicted on his shield. His grey <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">stallion</a> had silver-and-smoke trappings matching Abelar's attire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to a semi-canon source, he was heir to the ruling <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oldtown\" title=\"Lord of Oldtown\">Lord of Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.2C_2nd_edition.2C_.5B.5Blist_of_characters_and_arms_in_the_hedge_knight_graphic_novel_collection.7Croll_of_arms.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.2C_2nd_edition.2C_.5B.5Blist_of_characters_and_arms_in_the_hedge_knight_graphic_novel_collection.7Croll_of_arms.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> considered him to be an unexceptional <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of high birth and low skill.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abelar_Hightower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Abelar took part in the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Ashford_Meadow\" title=\"Tourney at Ashford Meadow\">tourney at Ashford Meadow</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>, where he challenged Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Valarr_Targaryen\" title=\"Valarr Targaryen\">Valarr Targaryen</a>, one of the tourney champions, in the first joust. Abelar and Valarr both broke lances against each other on the first tilt, but on the second, the prince knocked Abelar off his horse with a lance blow to the chest. Abelar's <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a> had to call two servingmen to carry the dazed knight off the field and back to his tent, the first of Valarr's nine victories against \"undistinguished foes\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abelar_Hightower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafabelar_hightower.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafabelar_hightower.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Abelar Hightower.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rthk.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.2C_2nd_edition.2C_.5B.5Blist_of_characters_and_arms_in_the_hedge_knight_graphic_novel_collection.7Croll_of_arms.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.2C_2nd_edition.2C_.5B.5Blist_of_characters_and_arms_in_the_hedge_knight_graphic_novel_collection.7Croll_of_arms.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">Graphic Novel</a>, 2nd edition, <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_characters_and_arms_in_The_Hedge_Knight_graphic_novel_collection\" title=\"List of characters and arms in The Hedge Knight graphic novel collection\">Roll of Arms</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403123555\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.081 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.279 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 700/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10651/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8858/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1732/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3193/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  265.443      1 -total\n 95.63%  253.833      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.13%  252.512      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.35%   27.484     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.67%   12.404      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.45%    9.171      6 Template:Ref\n  1.71%    4.543      6 Template:Ref/core\n  1.56%    4.152      1 Template:Date\n  0.93%    2.479      1 Template:References\n  0.46%    1.213      2 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:2681-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403123555 and revision id 333120\n -->\n",
